      "span_text": "Cell cytotoxicity and adhesion studies have shown that superparamagnetic iron oxide nanoparticles are toxic to human dermal fibroblasts, and their internalization results in disruption of the organization of the cytoskeleton in these cells. [CITATION_1]"
